  <refnamediv>
    <refname>Gallery</refname>

    <refpurpose>A gallery of low discrepancy sequences.</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>

  <refsection>
    <title>Purpose</title>

    <para>
      The goal of this page is to gather experiments showing 
	  2D pictures of low disrepancy sequences.
    </para>

  </refsection>

  <refsection>
    <title>Halton Sequence</title>

    <programlisting role="example">
      <![CDATA[
u=lowdisc_ldgen ( 1000 , 2 , "halton" );
scf(); 
plot(u(:,1),u(:,2),"bo")
xtitle("Halton: 1000 points","X1","X2")
   ]]>
    </programlisting>

    <para>
      The previous script produces the following output.
    </para>

    <para>
      <inlinemediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata
          fileref ="halton-s2-n1000.png"
          align ="center"
          valign ="middle"
			/>
        </imageobject>
      </inlinemediaobject>
    </para>

  </refsection>

